text: Sakineh Almasi (, born 1979) is an Iranian politician and the current member of the Parliament of Iran, representing Kangan, Jam, Dayyer and Asaluyeh district. She is also Vice President of Federation of War Veterans and Disabled Persons of Iran. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Members of the 10th Islamic Consultative Assembly Category:Moderation and Development Party politicians Category:Members of the Women's fraction of Islamic Consultative Assembly
